title: Double Eyelid False Eyelashes Makeup Glue Transparent
description: * Caution- For external use only. Avoid direct contact with eye.- If irritation occurs, rinse immediately with water or contact a physician.- Keep out of reach of children. Keep at room temperature.* How To Use- Apply Eyelash Adhesive along the bottom edge of the false eyelash and wait 10-15 seconds until transparent -- Do not apply directly to eyelids.- Apply false eyelashes near the upper lash line of your natural eyelashes and press ends in place. Wait for adhesive to completely dry before applying makeup.- May also be used to create double eyelids.
